{"words":[{"word":"mechascout","count":4},{"word":"unparalleled","count":3},{"word":"promised","count":2},{"word":"part","count":2},{"word":"i'll","count":2},{"word":"remember","count":2},{"word":"fault","count":1},{"word":"rookie","count":1},{"word":"mistake","count":1},{"word":"forgot","count":1},{"word":"install","count":1},{"word":"overload","count":1},{"word":"safety","count":1},{"word":"unit","count":1},{"word":"made","count":1},{"word":"self-destruct","count":1},{"word":"r-really","count":1},{"word":"feel","count":1},{"word":"better","count":1},{"word":"yes","count":1},{"word":"find","count":1},{"word":"cute","count":1},{"word":"masterful","count":1},{"word":"design","count":1},{"word":"especially","count":1},{"word":"tard-e","count":1},{"word":"head","count":1},{"word":"originally","count":1},{"word":"academy","count":1},{"word":"creation","count":1},{"word":"mission","count":1},{"word":"protect","count":1},{"word":"written","count":1},{"word":"deepest","count":1},{"word":"layer","count":1},{"word":"operational","count":1},{"word":"logic","count":1},{"word":"hear","count":1},{"word":"compliments","count":1},{"word":"course","count":1},{"word":"treat","count":1},{"word":"experience","count":1},{"word":"starting","count":1},{"word":"point","count":1},{"word":"research","count":1},{"word":"day","count":1},{"word":"create","count":1},{"word":"perfect","count":1},{"word":"erect","count":1},{"word":"statue","count":1},{"word":"honor","count":1},{"word":"memory","count":1},{"word":"mistakes","count":1},{"word":"aid","count":1},{"word":"wait","count":1},{"word":"deliver","count":1}],"lines":[{"text":"It's all my fault. A rookie mistake... I forgot to install the overload safety unit... I made it self-destruct...","quest_name":"Unparalleled Mechascout","quest_id":923700000},{"text":"I promised an Unparalleled Mechascout...","quest_name":"Unparalleled Mechascout","quest_id":923700000},{"text":"R-Really? You don't have to just say that to make me feel better...","quest_name":"Unparalleled Mechascout","quest_id":923700000},{"text":"Yes, you find it cute as well, don't you? That was my masterful design, especially the part with the TARD-E head!","quest_name":"Unparalleled Mechascout","quest_id":923700000},{"text":"After all, each part was originally an Academy creation. The mission to \"protect\" is written in the deepest layer of their operational logic.","quest_name":"Unparalleled Mechascout","quest_id":923700000},{"text":"If only it could hear your compliments...","quest_name":"Unparalleled Mechascout","quest_id":923700000},{"text":"Of course not! I'll treat this experience as the starting point of my research.","quest_name":"Unparalleled Mechascout","quest_id":923700000},{"text":"One day, I'll create an even more perfect Mechascout!","quest_name":"Unparalleled Mechascout","quest_id":923700000},{"text":"But before that, I want to erect a statue here. To honor its memory, to remember my mistakes, and to remember your aid.","quest_name":"Unparalleled Mechascout","quest_id":923700000},{"text":"Just wait and see. I promised you an Unparalleled Mechascout, and an Unparalleled Mechascout I <i>shall</i> deliver!","quest_name":"Unparalleled Mechascout","quest_id":923700000}]}